OL,3,CWoman has #2,000 stolen in so-called
OL,4,Cblessing scam
OL,6,FAn elderly woman had #2,000 stolen
OL,7,Ffrom her handbag after she fell victim
OL,8,Fto a 'blessing scam'.
OL,10,FThe woman, who has not been
OL,11,Fidentified, was approached by three
OL,12,Fwomen who claimed they could 'cleanse'
OL,13,Fher to combat things such as 'bad
OL,14,Fauras' and 'bad luck'.
OL,16,FWhen she handed her bag over it was
OL,17,Ftaken out of sight - with the women
OL,18,Fclaiming to be carrying out a
OL,19,F'ritual'. She later discovered that
OL,20,Fcash in her bag had been taken.
