OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) has
OL,7,Fissued a warning to the region's
OL,8,FChinese communities following the
OL,9,Fincident at around noon on 15 April.
OL,11,FThe forced added it was aware of
OL,12,F"these types of scams being reported
OL,13,Fboth nationally and around the world"
OL,14,F- with the latest victim targeted in
OL,15,Fthe Piccadilly area of the city.
OL,17,FOfficers have also released CCTV
OL,18,Fimages of three women they want to
OL,19,Fspeak to in connection with the theft.
