OL,6,FA spokesperson for GMP's City of
OL,7,FManchester team said: "We are aware
OL,8,Fthat these types of scams have been
OL,9,Freported both nationally and around
OL,10,Fthe world, and we want to make those
OL,11,Fwithin our Chinese communities aware
OL,12,Fthat people are exploiting their faith
OL,13,Fand goodwill to make money.
OL,15,F"If you know of anyone responsible for
OL,16,Fincidents similar to these, or have
OL,17,Fbeen the victim of a crime yourself,
OL,18,Fplease contact police via 101 or
OL,19,Fgmp.police.uk.
